Bundle the updated code
  npm run bundle

Build and run iOS
  npm run build-ios
  npm run run-ios

Start the web server:
  # Option 1: Using Python (serves from www directory)
  cd ~/www/WarDeckCordova/www && python3 -m http.server 8080
  # Access at: http://localhost:8080

  # Option 2: Using Cordova serve (shows project info page)
  cd ~/www/WarDeckCordova && npm run serve
  # Access at: http://localhost:8000/www/

  Stop the web server:

  # If using Python server:
  pkill -f "python3 -m http.server"

  # If using Cordova serve:
  pkill -f "cordova serve"

  # Or just press Ctrl+C in the terminal where the server is running

  Quick one-liner to start in background:

  # Start in background (add & at the end)
  cd ~/www/WarDeckCordova/www && python3 -m http.server 8080 &

  # Stop it later
  pkill -f "python3 -m http.server 8080"
